snippet.async_client:
import asyncio

from seed import AsyncSeedApi, Column

client = AsyncSeedApi(
    base_url="https://yourhost.com/path/to/api",
)


async def main() -> None:
    await client.dataservice.upload(
        columns=[
            Column(
                id="id",
                values=[1.1],
            )
        ],
    )


asyncio.run(main())
